OL,6,FShe mostly delivers the food herself
OL,7,Fon foot, bringing a taste of home to
OL,8,Fpeople of Ghanaian heritage in .
OL,10,FShe said: "Sometimes it's raining and
OL,11,Fyou need to go and deliver. You can't
OL,12,Fcancel because you need to keep the
OL,13,Fpeople coming. I don't have a car.
OL,15,F"When I get an order, I check the
OL,16,Fpostcode and if it is a 20 minute walk
OL,17,Fthen I'll deliver it. Anything more
OL,18,Fthan that, I have to call (the
OL,19,Fcustomer) and ask them to come and
OL,20,Fpick it up."
